

(Integration Documentation)
#######################Razorpay Integration####################################
1. Prerequisites
- Create Razorpay account  at  https://razorpay.com/
- Go to dashboard of Razorpay ("https://dashboard.razorpay.com/app/dashboard") and then select "Test Mode" .
- Go To Settings-> API Keys-> (then hit there to generate API "id" and "secret key").

2. Create Service at BM
-Create service as "razorpay.service.new"
-Also set profile data and credentials data in BM. At credentials tab use URL:https://api.razorpay.com/v1/orders   and also set secret key ,id at with your secret key ,id
-Set service with there "profile" and "credentials".


3.Create configuration/site preferences for following data
-razorId
-razorKey
-razorpayApikey
-razorEnable
-razorPayStoreName


5. Create "Processor" and "Payment method" at BM as "razorPay_Processor", "RAZORPAY" respectively

6.Use integration cartridge
-Use "int_razorpay" cartride in use code
-Also set cartridge path at BM site setting. Then hit the site.



